33namespace ZXing {
34namespace Pdf417 {
35
36static const int MODULES_IN_STOP_PATTERN = 18;
37
38static int GetMinWidth(const Nullable<ResultPoint>& p1, const Nullable<ResultPoint>& p2)
39{
40 if (p1 == nullptr || p2 == nullptr) {
41 // the division prevents an integer overflow (see below). 120 million is still sufficiently large.
42 return std::numeric_limits<int>::max() / CodewordDecoder::MODULES_IN_CODEWORD;
43 }
44 return std::abs(static_cast<int>(p1.value().x()) - static_cast<int>(p2.value().x()));
45}
46
47static int GetMinCodewordWidth(const std::array<Nullable<ResultPoint>, 8>& p)
48{
49 return std::min(std::min(GetMinWidth(p[0], p[4]), GetMinWidth(p[6], p[2]) * CodewordDecoder::MODULES_IN_CODEWORD / MODULES_IN_STOP_PATTERN),
50 std::min(GetMinWidth(p[1], p[5]), GetMinWidth(p[7], p[3]) * CodewordDecoder::MODULES_IN_CODEWORD / MODULES_IN_STOP_PATTERN));
51}
52
53static int GetMaxWidth(const Nullable<ResultPoint>& p1, const Nullable<ResultPoint>& p2)
54{
55 if (p1 == nullptr || p2 == nullptr) {
56 return 0;
57 }
58 return std::abs(static_cast<int>(p1.value().x()) - static_cast<int>(p2.value().x()));
59}
60
61static int GetMaxCodewordWidth(const std::array<Nullable<ResultPoint>, 8>& p)
62{
63 return std::max(std::max(GetMaxWidth(p[0], p[4]), GetMaxWidth(p[6], p[2]) * CodewordDecoder::MODULES_IN_CODEWORD / MODULES_IN_STOP_PATTERN),
64 std::max(GetMaxWidth(p[1], p[5]), GetMaxWidth(p[7], p[3]) * CodewordDecoder::MODULES_IN_CODEWORD / MODULES_IN_STOP_PATTERN));
65}
66
67DecodeStatus DoDecode(const BinaryBitmap& image, bool multiple, std::list<Result>& results)
68{
69 Detector::Result detectorResult;
70 DecodeStatus status = Detector::Detect(image, multiple, detectorResult);
71 if (StatusIsError(status)) {
72 return status;
73 }
74
75 for (const auto& points : detectorResult.points) {
76 DecoderResult decoderResult =
77 ScanningDecoder::Decode(*detectorResult.bits, points[4], points[5], points[6], points[7],
78 GetMinCodewordWidth(points), GetMaxCodewordWidth(points));
79 if (decoderResult.isValid()) {
80 auto point = [&](int i) { return points[i].value(); };
81 Result result(std::move(decoderResult), {point(0), point(2), point(3), point(1)}, BarcodeFormat::PDF_417);
82 result.metadata().put(ResultMetadata::ERROR_CORRECTION_LEVEL, decoderResult.ecLevel());
83 if (auto extra = decoderResult.extra()) {
84 result.metadata().put(ResultMetadata::PDF417_EXTRA_METADATA, extra);
85 }
86 results.push_back(result);
87 if (!multiple) {
88 return DecodeStatus::NoError;
89 }
90 }
91 else if (!multiple) {
92 return decoderResult.errorCode();
93 }
94 }
95 return results.empty() ? DecodeStatus::NotFound : DecodeStatus::NoError;
96}
97
98Result
99Reader::decode(const BinaryBitmap& image) const
100{
101 std::list<Result> results;
102 DecodeStatus status = DoDecode(image, false, results);
103 if (StatusIsOK(status)) {
104 return results.front();
105 }
106 return Result(status);
107}
108
109std::list<Result>
110Reader::decodeMultiple(const BinaryBitmap& image) const
111{
112 std::list<Result> results;
113 DoDecode(image, true, results);
114 return results;
115}
